<HEADLINE>
<P>
BARR STRIKES OUT SINGING THE ANTHEM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I was appalled and repulsed by the rude, thoughtless and inconsiderate 
performance of our national anthem by Roseanne Barr at Jack Murphy Stadium in 
San Diego. It wasn't bad enough that she agreed to "sing" in the first place 
knowing full well that she couldn't; but to follow her "performance" with an 
inappropriate gesture and spitting was totally unacceptable and an insult to 
those in the stadium and the rest of our great country as well. 
</P>
<P>
KATHLEEN A. CLEMENTS 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
