<HEADLINE>
<P>
BODY FOUND NEAR I-5 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The body of a woman was found Friday in the brush along the Main Street on-ramp 
to Interstate 5 in Chula Vista. 
</P>
<P>
The woman's identity was not available. 
</P>
<P>
A Border Patrol agent discovered the body at 2:55 p.m. and notified Chula Vista 
police, who called in the Metro Homicide Task Force, officials said. 
</P>
<P>
Police are investigating the death as a homicide or traffic fatality. 
</P>
<P>
No further information was available. 
</P>
