<SUBJECT>
<P>
MILITARY CONFRONTATIONS; IRAQ -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- KUWAIT; OIL PRICES; OIL 
INDUSTRY -- IRAQ; OIL INDUSTRY -- KUWAIT; OIL INDUSTRY -- UNITED STATES; 
