HISPANICS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; LOS ANGELES COUNTY BOARD OF SUPERVISORS; 
FLORES, SARAH; O'BRIEN, GREGORY JR; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- SUITS; AMERICAN CIVIL 
LIBERTIES UNION; MEXICAN AMERICAN LEGAL DEFENSE AND EDUCATIONAL FUND; RACIAL 
DISCRIMINATION; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- ELECTIONS -- 1990; POLITICAL CANDIDATES; 
