<P>
CALIFORNIA STATE UNIVERSITY; CALIFORNIA STATE UNIVERSITY BOARD OF TRUSTEES; 
STUDENT FEES; CALIFORNIA -- BUDGET; COLLEGES -- CALIFORNIA; COLLEGE STUDENTS; 
