IRVINE FIRM TO AID IN CHILD-CARE PLANNING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An Irvine consulting firm will help Ventura businesses develop child-care 
services for their employees for a second year. 
</P>
<P>
The Ventura City Council agreed earlier this week to again hire the Child Care 
Planning Associates for the three-year project. 
</P>
